Privacy Policy
BizFund App

At BizFund, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard the information you provide when using the BizFund app. By using the app, you consent to the practices described in this policy.
1. Information Collection
a)	Personal Information: When you register on the BizFund app, we collect certain personal information, including your name, email address, phone number, business name, type of business, location of the business, and desired capital to start or expand your business. This information is necessary for user identification and communication with you.
b)	Quiz Responses: We collect the quiz responses you provide during the daily business management quiz to assess your eligibility for start-up grants.
c)	Bonus Points: We collect data on your consistent follow-up and participation in the daily quiz challenges to award bonus points.
2. Use of Information
a)	Grant Allocation: Your quiz responses, bonus points, number of votes, and likes will be used to determine the allocation of start-up grants to deserving beneficiaries at the end of each month.
b)	Communication: We will use your email address and phone number to communicate with you regarding app-related matters, grant allocations, and any changes to our services.
c)	Statistical Analysis: We may perform statistical analyses to improve the app's functionality and user experience. Such analyses will be done using aggregated and anonymized data.
3. Information Sharing
a)	User Information: Your personal information, including your email address and phone number, will not be displayed or shared with anyone other than the app administration. We will never sell, rent, or trade your personal information.
b)	Business Information: Business-related information provided during registration may be shared with other users solely for the purpose of voting and liking quiz responses. However, this information will be displayed in an anonymized and aggregated manner.


4. User Conduct and Security
a.	User Conduct: As a user of the BizFund app, you are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account information, including your username and password. You must not share your account credentials with others or engage in any activity that compromises the security of the app.
b.	Security Measures: We employ industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration. However, no method of data transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
5. Legal Compliance
We may disclose your personal information if required to do so by law or if we believe that such action is necessary to comply with legal obligations, protect our rights or the rights of others, and ensure the safety and security of our users.
6. Children's Privacy
The BizFund app is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe that a child has provided us with their information, please contact us immediately, and we will take appropriate steps to remove the information from our records.
7. Changes to the Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes to the policy will be posted within the app, and your continued use of the app after such modifications will constitute your acceptance of the revised policy.
8. Contact Us
If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or your personal information, please contact us at:
arrianahtech@gmail.com / +254728842608

Effective Date: 31st July 2023
